{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-pm-event-list-demo",
    "name": "PM CE · testnet · categories & event/list",
    "description": "用户端 `GET /ce/pm/v1/api/categories` 与 `GET /ce/pm/v1/api/event/list` 契约测试（对齐 prediction-serv `CategoryController` / `EventController` / `MarketListReq`）。\n\nWiki：https://skyrocket.sg.larksuite.com/wiki/TEZgwnuyOiJ315kIRn1lypTZgce\n\n**源码要点（2026-06）**：分类 `i18nName` 始终返回（`lang=en` 取 i18n JSON 的 `en` key）；列表 `markets[].rules=null`；`outcomes` key 空格规整为下划线；体育盘口含 `sportsDisplayColumn`。\n\n**运行顺序**：先跑 `00 Setup`；`[err]` 为预期 `ret_code=10001`。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "https://api2-testnet.zoomex.com" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "30101", "description": "由 00 Setup 覆盖；无数据时回退默认值。" },
    { "key": "categoryId2", "value": "303", "description": "多选 / 逗号 categoryIds 辅助 id。" }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "if (!pm.request.headers.has('lang')) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'lang', value: 'zh-Hant' });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 Setup",
      "description": "从分类树解析可用叶子 `categoryId`，供 event/list 用例复用。",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "拉取分类树并写入 categoryId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('ret_code 为 0', () => pm.expect(body.ret_code).to.eql(0));",
                  "pm.test('result.tree 为数组', () => pm.expect(body.result.tree).to.be.an('array'));",
                  "function walk(nodes, fn) { (nodes || []).forEach(n => { fn(n); walk(n.children, fn); }); }",
                  "function pickLeafId(tree) {",
                  "  let prefer = null, any = null;",
                  "  walk(tree, (n) => {",
                  "    if (!n.isLeaf || n.id == null) return;",
                  "    any = String(n.id);",
                  "    if ((n.marketCount == null || n.marketCount > 0) && !prefer) prefer = String(n.id);",
                  "  });",
                  "  return prefer || any;",
                  "}",
                  "const picked = pickLeafId(body.result.tree);",
                  "if (picked) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('categoryId', picked);",
                  "  pm.test('已写入 categoryId=' + picked, () => pm.expect(picked).to.match(/^\\d+$/));",
                  "} else {",
                  "  pm.test('分类树为空时保留默认 categoryId', () => pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('categoryId')).to.be.ok);",
                  "}",
                  "const ids = [];",
                  "walk(body.result.tree, (n) => { if (n.isLeaf && n.id != null) ids.push(String(n.id)); });",
                  "if (ids.length > 1) pm.collectionVariables.set('categoryId2', ids[1]);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "lang", "value": "zh-Hant" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/ce/pm/v1/api/categories"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "A · GET /categories",
      "description": "`CategoryController#listCategories`：无 query；`lang` header 决定 i18n。",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('HTTP 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "const body = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('ret_code 为 0', () => pm.expect(body.ret_code).to.eql(0));",
              "pm.test('Responses 壳字段', () => {",
              "  pm.expect(body).to.include.keys('ret_code', 'ret_msg', 'result', 'time_now');",
              "});",
              "pm.test('result.tree 为数组', () => pm.expect(body.result.tree).to.be.an('array'));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "A01 默认结构（lang=zh-Hant）",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "function walk(nodes, fn) { (nodes || []).forEach(n => { fn(n); walk(n.children, fn); }); }",
                  "const tree = pm.response.json().result.tree;",
                  "pm.test('有节点时含 id / name', () => {",
                  "  if (!tree.length) return;",
                  "  walk(tree, (n) => { pm.expect(n).to.have.property('id'); pm.expect(n).to.have.property('name'); });",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('children 为数组或缺失', () => {",
                  "  walk(tree, (n) => { if (n.children != null) pm.expect(n.children).to.be.an('array'); });",
                  "});",
                  "const leaves = [];",
                  "walk(tree, (n) => { if (n.isLeaf) leaves.push(n); });",
                  "pm.test('繁中叶子返回 i18nName（有翻译时非空）', () => {",
                  "  if (!leaves.length) return;",
                  "  const withI18n = leaves.filter((n) => n.i18nName != null && String(n.i18nName).length > 0);",
                  "  pm.expect(withI18n.length, '至少一个叶子应有 i18nName').to.be.above(0);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "lang", "value": "zh-Hant" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/ce/pm/v1/api/categories"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "A02 header lang=en（i18nName 取 en key）",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const leaves = [];",
                  "function walk(nodes) { (nodes || []).forEach((n) => { if (n.isLeaf) leaves.push(n); walk(n.children); }); }",
                  "walk(pm.response.json().result.tree);",
                  "pm.test('lang=en 时叶子仍返回 i18nName（不再省略）', () => {",
                  "  if (!leaves.length) return;",
                  "  const withI18n = leaves.filter((n) => n.i18nName != null && String(n.i18nName).length > 0);",
                  "  pm.expect(withI18n.length, '英文也应从 i18n JSON en key 填充 i18nName').to.be.above(0);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('英文 i18nName 与 name 字段均存在', () => {",
                  "  if (!leaves.length) return;",
                  "  const n = leaves.find((x) => x.i18nName) || leaves[0];",
                  "  pm.expect(n).to.have.property('name');",
                  "  if (n.i18nName != null) pm.expect(n.i18nName).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "lang", "value": "en" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/ce/pm/v1/api/categories"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "A03 叶子节点字段（有数据时）",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const leaves = [];",
                  "function walk(nodes) { (nodes || []).forEach(n => { if (n.isLeaf) leaves.push(n); walk(n.children); }); }",
                  "walk(pm.response.json().result.tree);",
                  "pm.test('存在叶子时含 isLeaf / marketCount', () => {",
                  "  if (!leaves.length) return;",
                  "  const n = leaves[0];",
                  "  pm.expect(n.isLeaf).to.eql(true);",
                  "  pm.expect(n).to.have.property('marketCount');",
                  "  pm.expect(n.marketCount).to.be.a('number');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('叶子含 i18nName 字段（可为 null）', () => {",
                  "  if (!leaves.length) return;",
                  "  leaves.forEach((n) => pm.expect(n).to.have.property('i18nName'));",
                  "});"
                ]
